title: Administration
admin1-desc: He started our business and does his best to keep things running. Two-dimensional game fanatic.
admin2-desc: A chosen one, who with his dedication and loyalty earned himself the title of co-owner.
admin3-desc: A website and bot developer, a young who aims high and is constantly working on something new.
admin4-desc: Black character with whom there is no joke, his specific approach to things was appreciated by the owners.
admin5-desc: A creative person, gifted with imagination. He always tries to talk and engage at any events of the whole group. The friend of the lost sheep.
